Sephora’s Beauty Insider Spring Savings Event is finally here, meaning you can enjoy some major discounts on your fave beauty products.
The two-week sale is offering Beauty Insider members up to 20% off their entire order with the code SPRINGSAVE.
But your discount depends on your Beauty Insider level.
The sale is packed with deals on makeup, haircare, skincare and more from some of the most popular beauty brands.
And to offer you a little assistance with your deal hunting, we’ve gathered some of the best savings you can get during the beloved sale.